{"tid":2190470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★MTR Mobile 查詢「831」虛擬服務大使會解答 太子站 ，並附上地鐵路線","createTime":"2020-09-05T16:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T16:36:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e007b6d347442442628b35c65ff9cc3dad7cd823","tid":2190470,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】港鐵應用程式MTR Mobile內的Chatbot互動查詢功能運用AI技術，供市民查詢地鐵路線和資訊，只要在Chatbot輸入問題，虛擬服務大使「Macy」就會解答。不過有網民發現，輸入「831」時，Macy會直接匹配太子站，並附上地鐵路線。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，此功能以虛擬服務大使「Macy」，為乘客提供即時互動查詢功能，讓乘客更方便、快捷地搜尋有關港鐵站出入口等資訊。 Chatbot是運用港鐵自身的車站出入口資訊，結合市場上的公開資料，以提供車站周邊地標查詢。為確保Chatbot所提供的資料準確度，避免作出令人混淆的資訊，港鐵不時留意「Macy」的情況，當發現顯示結果有異常時，會適時跟進並作出調整。我們都留意到上述的情況，會作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n記者再嘗試在MTR Moblie的Chatbot查詢「831」，回答已更改為「唔好意思我唔明白，我仲一步步學緊。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/mtr-mobile-%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2-831-ai%E9%85%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-095500790.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fmtr-mobile-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2-831-ai%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599-095500790.html&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d07f97d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/mtr-mobile-%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2-831-ai%E9%85%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99-095500790.html</a>"},{"pid":"8640ac91f78e818f510b6b8a6a134f8dc0cb8162","tid":2190470,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a9Y7RUa2CIiKiK8.SuxLKw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/singtao.com.hk/c0145ca6ff856d73014e39d3882bf86c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fa9Y7RUa2CIiKiK8.SuxLKw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fc0145ca6ff856d7301